== 2009年国际足联联合会杯 ==
[[File:Vuvuzela_blower,_Final_Draw,_FIFA_2010_World_Cup.jpg|thumb]]
呜呜祖拉從[[2009年洲際國家杯|2009年洲際國家杯]]和[[2010年世界盃足球賽|2010年世界盃]]這兩個都在南非舉行的球賽中得到人們關注，[[國際足協|國際足協]]擔心這種聲音會成為[[足球流氓|足球流氓]]的武器，企業利用呜呜祖拉做廣告。[[南非足球協會|南非足球協會]]發表了一份簡報稱呜呜祖拉是南非球迷看球的必需品，<ref name=makhaye/>國際足聯在2008年7月決定，允許在世界球賽中使用呜呜祖拉。<ref>{{cite news |title=Fifa gives Vuvuzelas thumbs up |date=11/07/2008 |url=http://www.news24.com/xArchive/Sport/SWC2010/Fifa-gives-Vuvuzelas-thumbs-up-20080711 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-date=2019-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017085241/https://www.news24.com/xArchive/Sport/SWC2010/Fifa-gives-Vuvuzelas-thumbs-up-20080711 |dead-url=no }}</ref>國際足聯主席[[塞普·布拉特|塞普·布拉特]]反對禁止呜呜祖拉，他說，「我們不應該讓非洲世界盃歐洲化」<ref name="ESPN Soccernet">{{cite news|url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=656178&sec=global&cc=5901|title=Dutch coach joins chorus to ban vuvuzela|publisher=ESPN Soccernet|date=2009-06-20|accessdate=2009-06-20|archive-date=2012-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129065932/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=656178&sec=global&cc=5901|dead-url=no}}</ref>國際足聯允許在2010年世界盃足球賽中使用任何樂器，<ref>{{cite web |url= http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=661424&sec=worldcup2010&cc=3888 |title= FIFA give vuvuzela green light for World Cup |date= 2009-07-17 |accessdate= 2009-07-18 |archive-date= 2012-10-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20121021175858/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=661424&sec=worldcup2010&cc=3888 |dead-url= no }}</ref>除了一米以上的呜呜祖拉。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.bndestem.nl/sport/sportalgemeen/6815849/FIFA-verbiedt-lange-vuvuzelas.ece |title= FIFA verbiedt lange vuvuzela's |language= nl |date= 2010-06-10 |accessdate= 2010-06-10 |archive-date= 2010-06-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100613054718/http://www.bndestem.nl/sport/sportalgemeen/6815849/FIFA-verbiedt-lange-vuvuzelas.ece |dead-url= no }}</ref>

一些足球評論員、球員和國際觀眾爭論過關於反對在2009年國際足聯聯合會盃中使用呜呜祖拉。在義大利對美國的比賽中，[[BBC|BBC]]體育評論員[[李·迪臣|李·迪臣]]（Lee Michael Dixon）對呜呜祖拉「非常惱火」。

== 2010年世界杯足球赛 ==
2010年世界杯足球赛期间，韩国[[Hyundai|现代集团]]和当地一家名为“木星画廊（Jupiter Drawing Room）”的南非广告公司合作，在南非[[开普敦|开普敦市]]的一座未完工的[[高架桥|高架桥]]上面，架设了一个长达{{convert|114|ft|m}}能鸣叫的呜呜赛拉<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.chrisrawlinson.com/2010/06/hyundai-cape-town-giant-vuvuzela/ |title= Hyundai: Cape Town Giant Vuvuzela |last= Rawlinson |first= Chris |date= 2010-06-08 |work=  |publisher=  |accessdate= 2010-06-13 |archive-date= 2020-11-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201109035040/http://www.chrisrawlinson.com/2010/06/hyundai-cape-town-giant-vuvuzela/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。这个呜呜赛拉靠装在喇叭口上的几个[[气笛|气笛]]发出声响，每当世界杯足球赛的比赛要开场的时，它就会吹响喇叭。

=== 爭議 ===
==== 帶給比賽的困擾 ====
[[File:Vuvuzelas_Warning.jpg|right]]
在[[FIFA|FIFA]]收到许多来自欧洲电视传媒集团的投诉以后，这些集团希望呜呜祖拉被禁止，因为呜呜祖拉的声音覆盖了评论员的声音。在比赛之前，荷兰国家足球队教练[[范马尔维克|范马尔维克]]（Bert van Marwijk）和西班牙国家足球队中场球员[[哈維·阿隆索|哈維·阿隆索]]（Xabi Alonso）也呼吁，后者说，呜呜祖拉的声音让球员难以沟通和集中注意力，而且这对气氛没有很大的提升。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=656178&sec=global&cc=5901|title=Dutch coach joins chorus to ban vuvuzela|publisher=ESPN Soccernet|date=2009-06-20|accessdate=2009-06-20|archive-date=2012-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129065932/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=656178&sec=global&cc=5901|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/8106502.stm |title=Fifa to discuss vuvuzela future |date=2009-06-18 |publisher=BBC SPORT |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-date=2012-04-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66dbaM0Mj?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/8106502.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
2010年6月13日，BBC播报[[Danny_Jordaan|Danny Jordaan]]在比赛中对呜呜祖拉的禁止的考虑。<ref name="bbcponder">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2010/8737455.stm |title=World Cup 2010: South Africa ponders vuvuzela ban |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2010-06-13 |accessdate=2010-06-13 |archive-date=2014-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141203211758/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2010/8737455.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> Jordaan说到：“如果有必要，我们愿意「把携带呜呜赛拉的球迷驱逐出球场」”，并且“如果让赛场的球员为此引发不满，我们将采取果断措施。”<ref name="bbcponder"/>

在世界杯足球赛的开幕式上，播音员要求吹呜呜赛拉的球迷放低音量，否则其他观众无法听到他的播音<ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/WN/Media/fifa-world-cup-2010-opening-ceremony-kicks-off/story?id=10888477 |title=FIFA World Cup 2010: Opening Ceremony Kicks Off Tournament in South Africa - ABC News |publisher=Abcnews.go.com |date=2010-06-11 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-date=2019-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007035114/https://abcnews.go.com/WN/Media/fifa-world-cup-2010-opening-ceremony-kicks-off/story?id=10888477 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

赛事期间，许多球员都批评和抱怨呜呜赛拉所造成的噪音。其中，法国队的[[帕特里斯·埃夫拉|帕特里斯·埃夫拉]]（Patrice Evra）直接责难这种高音喇叭导致了他们球队发挥失准<ref name="bbcponder"/>。他还说到，从体育场传出来的呜呜赛拉的噪音让球员们在下榻处都无法正常休息<ref name="google1">{{cite web |author=(AFP) – 9 hours ago |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5ghUbctrzM88GqP_A_qJZppPbhjVw |title=AFP: World Cup organiser mulls vuvuzela ban |publisher=Google.com |date= |accessdate=2010-06-13 |archive-date=2010-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100614200930/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5ghUbctrzM88GqP_A_qJZppPbhjVw |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其余的批评还包括，阿根廷球员[[利昂内尔·梅西|利昂内尔·梅西]]（Lionel Messi）抱怨呜呜赛拉的声响妨碍了球员们在赛场上的正常沟通<ref>{{cite web |author=DPA |url=http://beta.thehindu.com/sport/football/article454621.ece |title=The Hindu : Sport / Football : It is impossible to communicate, it’s like being deaf: Messi |publisher=Beta.thehindu.com |date= |accessdate=2010-06-13 |archive-date=2010-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100726224333/http://beta.thehindu.com/sport/football/article454621.ece |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，而各家广播公司都抱怨他们评论员的说话声完全被呜呜赛拉的轰鸣给淹没了<ref name="google1"/>。葡萄牙队的[[基斯坦奴·朗拿度|C羅納度]]（Cristiano Ronaldo）也在采访中提到呜呜赛拉的噪音让整个球队无法集中精力于比赛<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rnw.nl/international-justice/bulletin/ronaldo-hits-out-vuvuzelas |title=Ronaldo hits out at vuvuzelas | Radio Netherlands Worldwide |publisher=Rnw.nl |date= |accessdate=2010-06-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100617160420/http://www.rnw.nl/international-justice/bulletin/ronaldo-hits-out-vuvuzelas |archivedate=2010-06-17 |df= }}</ref>。

很多电视观众抱怨，体育场内传出来的背景声效只剩下了呜呜赛拉的声音，而场内观众正常的欢叫声完全被压制了<ref name="nyp1">{{cite news | title=Buzz off, vuvuzelas! | publisher=New York Post | url=http://www.nypost.com/p/sports/more_sports/buzz_off_vuvuzelas_FPa9BYlmlRWJMsF1W65cyJ?CMP=OTC-rss&FEEDNAME= | first=Elio | last=Valenti | date=2010-06-13 | accessdate=2010-06-15 | archive-date=2010-06-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100617162330/http://www.nypost.com/p/sports/more_sports/buzz_off_vuvuzelas_FPa9BYlmlRWJMsF1W65cyJ?CMP=OTC-rss&FEEDNAME= | dead-url=no }}</ref>。一名[[ESPN|ESPN]]发言人说，他们会采取措施在他们的球赛直播中降低呜呜赛拉造成的噪音<ref>{{cite web|title=Organizers consider silencing vuvuzelas|url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/world-cup/story/_/id/5282269/ce/us/organizers-consider-silencing-vuvuzelas&cc=5901?ver=us|publisher=ESPN Soccernet|accessdate=2010-06-14|archive-date=2010-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100616164928/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/world-cup/story/_/id/5282269/ce/us/organizers-consider-silencing-vuvuzelas%26cc%3D5901?ver=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。也有些人认为，那些在开赛前演奏国歌期间所发出的呜呜赛拉的噪音根本就是一种亵渎的行为<ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/Media/vuvuzela-banned-world-cup/story?id=10908539 |title=Could the Vuvuzela Be Banned From World Cup? at |publisher=Abcnews.go.com |date= |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-date=2020-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213031949/https://abcnews.go.com/International/Media/vuvuzela-banned-world-cup/story?id=10908539 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sport24.co.za/Soccer/WorldCup/TournamentNews/Raucous-vuvuzela-here-to-stay-20100607 |title=Raucous vuvuzela here to stay: Sport: Sport: 2010 World Cup: Tournament News |publisher=Sport24.co.za |date=2010-06-07 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-date=2020-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908081056/https://www.news24.com/Sport/Raucous-vuvuzela-here-to-stay-20100607 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。其余的批评还提到，有些吹鸣呜呜赛拉的更像是为了表达对对方球队支持者的足球文化的蔑视<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.timeslive.co.za/opinion/letters/article502285.ece/Vuvuzela-drowns-out-diversity-of-soccer-songs |title=Vuvuzela drowns out diversity of soccer songs |publisher=Times LIVE |date= |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-date=2011-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110219033217/http://www.timeslive.co.za/opinion/letters/article502285.ece/Vuvuzela-drowns-out-diversity-of-soccer-songs |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一名德国音效工程师制作了一个45分钟的MP3声响下载文件，放到网路上销售。据称，它能在比赛电视直播期间对呜呜赛拉所发出的噪音起到“主动降噪”的作用。然而其他科学家对此并不乐观，怀疑其作用<ref>{{cite web |last=Moore |first=Matthew |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup-2010/7826995/World-Cup-2010-anti-vuvuzela-filter-could-cancel-out-noise-of-horns.html |title=World Cup 2010: 'anti-vuvuzela filter' could cancel out noise of horns at |publisher=Telegraph.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-date=2010-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100618052302/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup-2010/7826995/World-Cup-2010-anti-vuvuzela-filter-could-cancel-out-noise-of-horns.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="BBCnewsmagblockblare">{{cite web|title=Can you block out the blare of vuvuzelas?|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/magazine/8738604.stm|publisher=BBC News Magazine|accessdate=2010-06-15}}</ref>。

==== 對呜呜祖拉的支持 ====
有不少评论员认为呜呜赛拉是南非足球文化独特的组成部分，而且为比赛增添了气氛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sport24.co.za/Soccer/WorldCup/My2010WorldCup/Hands-off-our-Vuvuzelas-20100614|title=Hands off our Vuvuzelas|last=Matjila|first=Tsepho|work=Sport24|date=2010-06-14|accessdate=2010-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722052305/http://www.sport24.co.za/Soccer/WorldCup/My2010WorldCup/Hands-off-our-Vuvuzelas-20100614|archive-date=2011-07-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.busrep.co.za/index.php?fSectionId=561&fArticleId=5512478|title=Vuvuzela gives reverberating feel to soccer|work=Business Report|date=2010-06-14|last=Khanyile|first=Slindile|accessdate=2010-06-14}}{{Dead link|date=2020年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]的体育评论员Farayi Mungazi认为，这种喇叭的声音是“南非足球的标识音”，而且“能让人体验到南非足球的精髓”。他认为把世界杯带到非洲的同时“要当地人强行接受所谓的欧洲风格”是完全徒劳的<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/africa/8108691.stm|title=In defence of the vuvuzela|work=BBC Sport|date=2009-06-19|last=Mungazi|first=Farayi|accessdate=2010-06-14|archive-date=2020-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316025114/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/8108691.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的首席体育记者Paul Kelso将对呜呜赛拉的责难描绘为“煞风景”，并认为那些人应当“停止唠叨”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.telegraph.co.uk/sport/paulkelso/100009428/world-cup-hoooonnnk-its-time-for-killjoys-to-stop-moaning-and-embrace-the-vuvuzelaoo/|title=World Cup: Hoooonnnk! Its time for killjoys to stop moaning and embrace the vuvuzelaoo|work=Telegraph Blogs|last=Kelso|first=Paul|date=2010-06-14|accessdate=2010-06-14|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213219/http://blogs.telegraph.co.uk/sport/paulkelso/100009428/world-cup-hoooonnnk-its-time-for-killjoys-to-stop-moaning-and-embrace-the-vuvuzelaoo/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

针对批评，世界足协主席[[塞普·布拉特|塞普·布拉特]]（Sepp Blatter）回应道：“我早已说过，非洲有着不同的旋律，不同的声音。我不乐见球迷们在自己的国家中被禁止使用他们传统的音乐习俗。你们愿意见到你们的球迷在自己的国家中被禁止按照传统的习俗进行庆祝吗？”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metro.co.uk/sport/830884-vuvuzelas-defended-via-twitter-by-fifa-boss-sepp-blatter|title=Vuvuzelas defended via Twitter by Fifa boss Sepp Blatter|work=metro.co.uk Sports|date=2010-06-14|accessdate=2010-06-15|archive-date=2012-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002194335/http://www.metro.co.uk/sport/830884-vuvuzelas-defended-via-twitter-by-fifa-boss-sepp-blatter|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 在足球比賽以外的使用 ====
在一些購物中心禁止吹呜呜祖拉<ref>[http://www.ewn.co.za/articleprog.aspx?id=41683 No vuvuzelas inside Sandton City] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ewn.co.za/articleprog.aspx?id=41683 |date=20111006054626 }} ''Eyewitness News''</ref>。一些世界级别球員抱怨，他們在賓館房間裡被這種樂器打擾<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2010/article-1286491/WORLD-CUP-2010-Vuvuzelas-wont-banned-insist-South-Africa-chiefs.html WORLD CUP 2010: Vuvuzelas are here to stay - so show them some respect, insist tournament chiefs] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2010/article-1286491/WORLD-CUP-2010-Vuvuzelas-wont-banned-insist-South-Africa-chiefs.html |date=20201109040352 }} ''Daily Mail''</ref>。從而加大了他們對耳塞的需求，以防在世界盃其間損傷聽力<ref>{{cite web |author=Luphert Chilwane |url=http://www.businessday.co.za/articles/Content.aspx?id=111728 |title=Worried fans right to seek ear plugs, says Phonak at |publisher=Businessday.co.za |date=2010-06-11 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-date=2012-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120403040130/http://www.businessday.co.za/articles/Content.aspx?id=111728 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。耳塞在很多藥店供不應求，塑料呜呜祖拉的製造商尼尔范斯卡尔奎克開始向球迷出售耳塞<ref>[http://www.sport24.co.za/Soccer/WorldCup/NationalNews/Vuvuzelas-unplugged-for-some-20100611 Vuvuzelas unplugged for some] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sport24.co.za/Soccer/WorldCup/NationalNews/Vuvuzelas-unplugged-for-some-20100611 |date=20110722052239 }} ''Sport24''</ref>。

在香港，[[2012年香港政治制度改革|政改方案]]在[[香港立法會|香港立法會]]被進行表決，示威者在立法會外使用嗚嗚祖拉示威，當官員（如[[林瑞麟|林瑞麟]]）、建制派和[[民主黨_(香港)|民主黨]]議員發言時，就吹起嗚嗚祖拉<ref>http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/100623/4/itci.html{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。美國有人召集100人在[[BP|BP]]總部外吹嗚嗚祖拉抗議[[墨西哥灣|墨西哥灣]]的[[漏油|漏油]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/100702/8/iycr.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100707133625/http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/100702/8/iycr.html |archivedate=2010-07-07 }}</ref>[[台灣|台灣]]的[[泛綠|泛綠]]陣營也有人上街以嗚嗚祖拉反對[[ECFA|ECFA]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/100623/4/it7k.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100702223205/http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/100623/4/it7k.html |archivedate=2010-07-02 }}</ref>這都是在南非世界盃舉行期間發生的。

